ğŸŒ A10:2021 â€“ Server-Side Request Forgery (SSRF)
Q19. Define SSRF.
A: When an attacker causes the server to send HTTP requests to arbitrary locations (internal or external) by abusing a URLâ€‘fetch feature.

Q20. How to prevent SSRF?

